---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Help & FAQ | GOSQO" description="Installation, troubleshooting, billing, and privacy requests.">
  <h1>Help & FAQ</h1>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Installation</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Install the app in Shopify admin.</li>
      <li>Approve required permissions.</li>
      <li>Enable the Theme App Extension to activate the live chat widget.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Uninstallation</h2>
    <p>Uninstall from Shopify admin. Data handling follows the Privacy Policy.</p>

    <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Widget not visible: verify the Theme App Extension is enabled and published.</li>
      <li>Access issues: confirm permissions were granted during install.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Billing</h2>
    <p>Subscriptions are managed through Shopify billing.</p>

    <h2>Data requests</h2>
    <p>privacy@gosqo.com</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>